Piet gnome sort - represented as pseudocode for the visual language:
push 0 (i=0)
push 10 (n=10)
loop_start:
  dup i, dup n
  greater_equal? -> exit
  dup i
  push 0, equal? -> advance
  get arr[i], get arr[i-1]
  greater_equal? -> advance
  swap arr[i] with arr[i-1]
  decrement i -> loop_start
advance:
  increment i -> loop_start
exit:
